EN: Entrepreneurship is like an adventure, full of unknown risks.

ZH: 我们的公司成立伊始，就面临了很多创业难题。
EN: Our company faced many entrepreneurship challenges from the beginning.

ZH: 大学毕业后，我决定尝试创业。
EN: After graduating from college, I decided to try my hand at entrepreneurship.

ZH: 创业不仅要有勇气，还需要有谋略。
EN: Entrepreneurship requires not only courage, but also strategy.

ZH: 在创业的过程中，失败是难以避免的。
EN: Failure is inevitable in the process of entrepreneurship.

ZH: 创业者需要具备坚韧不拔的品质。
EN: Entrepreneurs need to have the quality of being tenacious.

ZH: 每个创业者都有自己的梦想和愿景。
EN: Every entrepreneur has their own dreams and visions.

ZH: 创业可以让人实现自己的抱负。
EN: Entrepreneurship can help people realize their ambitions.

